title: Sparkling Rain
lyrics:
Paroles de la chanson Sparkling Rain par Dita Von Teese
I'm on the roof sky
Turning a blind eye
Turbulent flow
Just let it go

Here comes the black shine
Blushing my light
Discoloured tones
Magical shadow

Fly
Fly
Fly to the rainbow
I'm in, You're out Don't you go ?

Hot sparkling rain

My bubbles unchained!
My pleasure Champagne
Again and again

Kaleidoscopic hallucinations
Coloring my lips
With delectation

Fly
Fly
Fly to the rainbow
I'm in, You're out Don't you go ?
